#  Material 3 Design System - Quick Reference

##  Color Palette

### Light Theme
```kotlin
// Primary Colors
Color(0xFFFF9494)  // CoralPink - Primary buttons, main stats
Color(0xFFFFD1D1)  // MediumPink - Secondary accents
Color(0xFFFFE3E1)  // LightPink - Tertiary elements
Color(0xFFFFF5E4)  // Cream - Backgrounds & cards

// Status Colors
Color(0xFF4CAF50)  // AttendancePresent - Green
Color(0xFFFF5252)  // AttendanceAbsent - Red  
Color(0xFFFF9800)  // AttendanceLate - Orange
```

### Dark Theme
```kotlin
Color(0xFFB86B6B)  // DarkCoralPink
Color(0xFF5A4040)  // DarkMediumPink
Color(0xFF4A3838)  // DarkPink
Color(0xFF3A3530)  // DarkCream
```

---

##  Typography Scale

```kotlin
// Large Headlines (Screen Titles)
MaterialTheme.typography.headlineLarge
// 32sp, Bold, 0.0 letter spacing

// Small Headlines (Section Headers)
MaterialTheme.typography.headlineSmall  
// 24sp, Bold, 0.0 letter spacing

// Dialog Titles
MaterialTheme.typography.titleLarge
// 22sp, SemiBold, 0.0 letter spacing

// Card Titles
MaterialTheme.typography.titleMedium
// 16sp, SemiBold, 0.15 letter spacing

// Body Text
MaterialTheme.typography.bodyMedium
// 14sp, Normal, 0.25 letter spacing

// Labels & Badges
MaterialTheme.typography.labelMedium
// 12sp, Medium, 0.5 letter spacing
```

---

##  Spacing System

```kotlin
// Tight spacing (badges, chips)
.padding(8.dp)

// List item spacing
verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(12.dp)

// Standard screen padding
.padding(16.dp)

// Section spacing
verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(24.dp)
```

---

##  Shapes & Corners

```kotlin
// Small components (badges, chips)
shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.small  // ~4dp

// Medium components (text fields, buttons)
shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.medium  // ~8dp

// Large components (cards, dialogs)
shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.large  // ~12dp
```

---

##  Component Templates

### Card
```kotlin
Card(
    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
    elevation = CardDefaults.cardElevation(defaultElevation = 2.dp),
    colors = CardDefaults.cardColors(
        containerColor = Color(0xFFFFF5E4)
    ),
    shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.large
) {
    // Content with 16.dp padding
    Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp)) {
        // ...
    }
}
```

### Dialog
```kotlin
AlertDialog(
    onDismissRequest = onDismiss,
    icon = {
        Icon(Icons.Default.IconName, contentDescription = "Description")
    },
    title = {
        Text("Title", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleLarge)
    },
    text = { /* Content */ },
    confirmButton = {
        Button(onClick = { }) { Text("Confirm") }
    },
    dismissButton = {
        TextButton(onClick = onDismiss) { Text("Cancel") }
    },
    shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.large
)
```

### Text Field
```kotlin
OutlinedTextField(
    value = value,
    onValueChange = { value = it; error = "" },
    label = { Text("Label") },
    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
    isError = error.isNotEmpty() && value.isBlank(),
    singleLine = true,
    shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.medium
)
```

### Top App Bar
```kotlin
TopAppBar(
    title = {
        Text("Title", style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleLarge)
    },
    navigationIcon = {
        IconButton(onClick = { }) {
            Icon(Icons.Default.ArrowBack, contentDescription = "Back")
        }
    },
    actions = {
        IconButton(onClick = { }) {
            Icon(Icons.Default.Action, contentDescription = "Action")
        }
    },
    colors = TopAppBarDefaults.topAppBarColors(
        containerColor = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primaryContainer,
        titleContentColor = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onPrimaryContainer
    )
)
```

### Badge Label
```kotlin
Surface(
    color = Color(0xFFFF9494),
    shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.small
) {
    Text(
        text = "Label:",
        style = MaterialTheme.typography.labelMedium,
        color = Color.White,
        modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 8.dp, vertical = 4.dp)
    )
}
```

### Empty State
```kotlin
Column(
    horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally,
    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(16.dp)
) {
    Icon(
        Icons.Default.IconName,
        contentDescription = "Description",
        modifier = Modifier.size(64.dp),
        tint = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.outline
    )
    Text(
        text = "No items yet",
        style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleLarge,
        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant
    )
    Text(
        text = "Helpful guidance text",
        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodyMedium,
        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant
    )
}
```

### List with Animation
```kotlin
LazyColumn(
    modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp),
    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(12.dp)
) {
    items(items, key = { it.id }) { item ->
        AnimatedVisibility(
            visible = true,
            enter = expandVertically(animationSpec = tween(300)) + fadeIn(),
            exit = shrinkVertically(animationSpec = tween(300)) + fadeOut()
        ) {
            ItemCard(item)
        }
    }
}
```

---

## ♿ Accessibility Guidelines

### Icons
```kotlin
// Always add contentDescription
Icon(
    Icons.Default.IconName,
    contentDescription = "Clear description of icon purpose"
)
```

### Interactive Elements
```kotlin
// Make hit targets at least 48.dp
IconButton(onClick = { }) {
    Icon(Icons.Default.Icon, contentDescription = "...")
}
```

### Color Contrast
- Text on CoralPink: Use White
- Text on Cream: Use Color(0xFF3A3530)
- Error text: Use MaterialTheme.colorScheme.error

---

##  Animation Timing

```kotlin
// Standard animations
animationSpec = tween(300)  // 300ms for most transitions

// Enter animations
enter = expandVertically(animationSpec = tween(300)) + fadeIn()

// Exit animations  
exit = shrinkVertically(animationSpec = tween(300)) + fadeOut()
```

---

##  Best Practices

1. **Always use MaterialTheme.colorScheme** for dynamic theming
2. **Use MaterialTheme.typography** for consistent text styles
3. **Add contentDescription** to all Icons
4. **Use MaterialTheme.shapes** for rounded corners
5. **Follow spacing system**: 8dp, 12dp, 16dp, 24dp
6. **Add animations** for list items and state changes
7. **Provide empty states** with guidance
8. **Confirm destructive actions** with dialogs
9. **Clear errors on input change** in forms
10. **Test in both light and dark modes**

---

##  Common Patterns

### Delete Confirmation
```kotlin
var showDeleteDialog by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }

// In composable
IconButton(onClick = { showDeleteDialog = true }) {
    Icon(Icons.Default.Delete, contentDescription = "Delete")
}

if (showDeleteDialog) {
    AlertDialog(
        // ... confirmation dialog
    )
}
```

### Form Validation
```kotlin
var value by remember { mutableStateOf("") }
var error by remember { mutableStateOf("") }

// In dialog confirmButton
Button(
    onClick = {
        when {
            value.isBlank() -> error = "Field is required"
            else -> {
                // Process
                onDismiss()
            }
        }
    }
)
```

